### Root 
GET http://localhost:8080/ HTTP/1.1

### Get Classroom
GET http://localhost:8080/classroom/1A HTTP/1.1

### Save Classroom
POST http://localhost:8080/classroom/save HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "roomName": "2A"
}

### Save and redirect Classroom
POST http://localhost:8080/classroom/saveandredirect HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "roomName": "2B"
}

### Get Student
GET http://localhost:8080/student/John HTTP/1.1

### Get Students by Class
GET http://localhost:8080/student/class/1A HTTP/1.1

### Save Student
POST http://localhost:8080/student/save HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Jane1",
    "score": 65,
    "classroomName": "1A"
}
